<p>Enjoy the shows!</p>"
"27","Hear Complete Live Show Online","Mike","2013-04-27 00:00:00","<p>We just posted our entire live show last night. You can hear the entire show on <a href=""http://snd.sc/ZOuiX6"" target=""_blank"">soundcloud</a>.</p>

<p>Martyr's is one of our favorite venues in Chicago. Lately, they've been using us as openers for bigger local and touring acts. We had the honor of opening for Leadfoot at their CD release party.</p>

